      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/624840845_18088941700869459_3450274478877835453_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=101&amp;ig_cache_key=MzIwNzUyMzAzMzQzMzU5MDc1Mg%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjk2OXg5NzEuc2RyLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=twS7jn62nkoQ7kNvwF7qPKV&amp;_nc_oc=Adpfx7jcMP9tSGPmVOCkBYUDIV9TR7hBjturXjUJaU-BIGHIl8xYGUvyUXH_jbgfTes&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=8&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=Dsf1oA_khHFHdl57l7Y6DA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyhvE9Ra9a9bU6fltK4GvZ0aofADgxt0YA3ZsHEY_rbAw&amp;oe=69C8D449" alt="Instagram billede fra @caecilietrier" /></p><p><strong>@caecilietrier</strong></p><p>My album Vind is out today<br/>
<br/>
Dedicated to Jannis Noya Makrigiannis<br/>
<br/>
Written and performed by Cæcilie Trier <br/>
Mixed by Jakob Littauer <br/>
Produced by Jakob Littauer and Cæcilie Trier<br/>
Mastered by Enyang Urbiks <br/>
Recorded by Jakob Littauer, Malthe Lund Madsen, Neil Young and Cæcilie Trier<br/>
<br/>
Jaleh Negari plays daf on ‘Gate’ and ‘Getting lost’ <br/>
Dawda Jobarteh plays on kora on ‘Hold you’ <br/>
Ned Ferm plays flute on ‘Hold you’ <br/>
Rune Kielsgård plays cymbals on ‘Hold you’<br/>
<br/>
Released by 15 love<br/>
<br/>
Artwork by Frederik Worm  <br/>
<br/>
Thank you for listening<br/>
<br/>
Supported by @kodakultur</p>]]></description>
